Introduction

D-CRUNCH (also known as Diamond Crunch) is an 8 member boy group that debuted under All-S Company, on August 6, 2018, with the single album "0806". The group currently consists of O.V, Hyunwook, Hyunho, Hyunoh, Minhyuk, Chanyoung, Dylan, and Jeongseung. On February 5, 2020, all the members signed under Ai Grand Korea, after their contracts with All-S Company expired. Hyunwoo officially departed the group on December 28th, 2020.

On November 9th, 2022 AIG announced on their official Fan Cafe that the group has disbanded.
